snippet.title: Astellia - Grand Adventure Trailer
snippet.description:
Get your own first look here: https://www.astellia-mmo.com/

Astellia Online is a Classical MMORPG striving to return the genre to its roots. Set in a vibrant fantasy world, Astellians are heroes blessed by the stars to call upon magical allies known as Astels. Join us on an adventure through harrowing dungeons, across epic battlefields, and write your story amongst the stars.

Official Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AstelliaOfficial-212166486213259
Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/AstelliaOnline
